\id RUT - Mbula
\h Rut
\toc3 Rut
\toc2 Rut
\toc1 Rut
\mt2 Malǝmce mala
\mt1 Rut
\imt1 Mǝncau
\im Kǝɓicau dorǝpwala aɓa Malǝmce mala \bk Rut\bk* ka, pur aɓalǝ anza mǝkwane mǝnana à bang cau malea aɓa \bk Malǝmce mala aKasǝla\bk* ka. Rut ɓwama Mowap ka al ɓwa Isǝrayila. Lang ɓwabure wù ka, Rut lǝmdǝ domǝsǝcau mǝnana à kǝ̀ gandǝ kume ɓàɓà raka aban nkili ɓwama Isǝrayila, sǝ lǝmdǝ paɓamuru mǝgule aban Ɓakuli mala Isǝrayila. A masǝlǝate ka, kum bǝsa bura atà aɓǝla mala burí mǝnana wuna ka, sǝ atàcau mala doɓala man sǝ duk kau mala Dauda, murǝm mǝgule mala Isǝrayila.
\ip Akǝɓicau mǝnana aɓa malǝmce mala \bk aKasǝla\bk* ka, à lǝmdǝ gir'murmwana mǝnana kǝ kum aɓwana mala Ɓakuli, yi mana ɓǝà pǝlì Ɓakuli nzǝmia ka.
\ip Malǝmce mala \bk Rut\bk* ka, kǝ lǝmdǝ tsǝkbu mǝnana yiu amur ɓwa'kúnɗàngna mǝnana pǝlǝa aban Ɓakuli mala Isǝrayila, sǝ yi duk mwashat atà aɓwana amǝ'mǝsǝcaunì male ka.
\iot Agir mǝnana a ɓalǝi ka
\io1 Naomi nyar a Betalami andǝ Rut \ior 1:1-22\ior*
\io1 Rut je andǝ Boaz \ior 2:1--3:18\ior*
\io1 Boaz al Rut \ior 4:1-22\ior*
\c 1
\s1 Elimelek andǝ ɓala male o a nzali Mowap
\p 
\v 1 Ɗiɗyal arǝ abákú mǝnana akasǝla kǝ yálmúrû ka, nzal-gula kpa aɓa nzali Isǝrayila. Sǝ ɓè ɓwabura ɓwa Betalami a bu-nzali Yahuda wari a nzali Mowap ace do abanì bǝti; wari andǝ māmí andǝ amuna-burana male ɓari.
\v 2 Lullǝ ɓwabure ama Elimelek, sǝ lullǝ māmí ama Naomi; lullǝ amuna-burana male nda ka Malon andǝ Kiliyon. Yià ka amǝ'Efǝrat\f + \fr 1:2 \fq amǝ'Efǝrat \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Tite 35:19; 1Sam 17:12; 1Kpa 4:4; Mik 5:2\xt*\ft .\f* mala Betalami a bu-nzali Yahuda na. Yì ka do a Betalami a bu-nzali Yahuda. À kùtí aɓa nzali Mowap sǝ à ue kam.
\v 3 Lang à ndaban do kano ka, Elimelek bura Naomi paklú, sǝ Naomi ueo andǝ amuna-burana male ɓari.
\v 4 Malon andǝ Kiliyon al amamǝna mala amǝ'Mowap. Alullǝ amālia nda ka Orpa andǝ Rut. Anzǝm apǝlǝa kǝla lum ngga,
\v 5 Malon andǝ Kiliyon gbal ka à paklú, sǝ Naomi ue nǝmurǝi, burí andǝ amuna-burana male pà kàm ɗàng.
\s1 Naomi andǝ Rut nyar a Betalami
\p 
\v 6 Naomi ok a bu-nzali Mowap ama Yahweh yina aban aɓwana male, yi pania wia girlina; nda Naomi gilǝki atwalo male ace mǝnana yì andǝ ankili-mǝɓwame ka, à nǝ̀ nyarî nzali Mowap.
\v 7 À bwal njar atārǝia andǝ ankili-mǝɓwame à nǝ̀ nyar a bu-nzali Yahuda, sǝama a njar aban o ka,
\v 8 Naomi banggi ankili-mǝɓwame ama, <<Wu nyar a là wu kya do wunǝ anggea wun. Ɓǝ̀ Yahweh pàkka wun mǝɓoarne kǝla mǝnana wu pàkkam, sǝ wu pàkkî aɓwana mǝnana à wuna ka.
\v 9 Sǝ ɓǝ̀ Yahweh tsǝa koyan atà wun ɓǝ̀ dukɓala ɗǝm, sǝ ɓǝ̀ pe wi usǝlǝo a ɓala mala burí.>>
\p Naomi pǝlǝa kùria-zǝp sǝ tsǝiandà. Sǝama à tita ɓua,
\v 10 à ne wi ama, <<Awo! Sǝm nǝ̀ ká atò, aban aɓwana mô.>>
\p 
\v 11 Naomi nyesǝia wia ama, <<Wu nyare, amuna-mamǝna mem. Palang sǝ wu earce ama wun nǝ̀ yiu atàm? Wu kǝ sǝni kǝla mǝ nǝ gandǝnǝ ɓǝla wun amuna-burana ɗǝm mǝnana à nǝ̀ al wun ngga le?
\v 12 Wu nyare a là, amuna-mamǝna mem, acemǝnana ǝn eni dolabura. Ko ɓǝ̀ ǝn twali ama tsǝkɓalǝu na kam piu, sǝ ǝn albura yalung, ǝn kum amuna-burana ka,
\v 13 wun nǝ̀ kúndǝia she ɓǝà gulkina ka le? Wun nǝ̀ ginǝ albura acea? Awo, amuna-mamǝna mem, wu sǝlǝna ama mǝno ka pà nǝ̀ pàk ɗàng. Bù Yahweh pǝlǝna arǝàm, sǝ mǝ nda aɓa bumkiɗikea kǝ̀rkǝ́r ace wun.>>
\p 
\v 14 Nyare à kùtí a ɓua. Pǝlǝa Orpa tsǝk nkili-mǝɓwame andà, sǝ nyar a là, sǝama Rut ka lanzǝ arǝ Naomi.
\v 15 Nda Naomi ne Rut ama, <<Sǝni, ɓio nyarna umǝna aban aɓwana male andǝ aɓakuli male. Wu nyar wunǝi a là.>>
\p 
\v 16 Sǝ Rut earî wi ama, <<Ida, kǝa banggam mǝ nyio ɗàng! Ɗekiam mǝ o atò. Ban mǝnana kat awu nǝ kà kam ngga, mǝ nǝ ká; ban mǝnana kat a duk kam ngga, mǝ nǝ do. Aɓwana mô nǝ̀ duk aɓwana mem, sǝ Ɓakuli mô nǝ̀ duk Ɓakuli mem.
\v 17 Ban mǝnana a wú ka, akàm sǝ mǝ nǝ wú, sǝ abanì sǝ à nǝ̀ tsǝk-luem. Ɓǝ̀ ɓashi mǝkǝ̀rkǝ́rnì mala Yahweh sulǝ amuram, ɓǝ̀ ǝn nying ɓekǝ gìr gau nrem sǝnǝ we ka, she lú!>>
\p 
\v 18 Lang Naomi sǝni ama Rut shamabumi nǝ̀ o atè ka, nyare ne wi kǝ cau ɗǝm ɗàng.
\p 
\v 19 Yià kǝm à lidǝmba nǝ gya ba yiu malea a Betalami. Lang à kùtí aɓa Betalami ka, là kat cam nǝ kusǝi acea, sǝ amamǝna mǝnana a lě ka, ɗìban ama, <<Naomi nda mǝnia?>>
\p 
\v 20 Naomi nyesǝia wia ama, <<Wu kǝa tunǝam ɗǝm ama Naomi\f + \fr 1:20 \ft Naomi ka ɓālǝi nda mǝɓoarne.\f* ɗàng; wu tunǝam ama Mara,\f + \fr 1:20 \ft Mara ka ɓālǝi nda mǝlulle.\f* acemǝnana Ɓakuli mana Karban nǝ Gulo kat ka, tsǝ̀ngŋǝ̀nà do mem pǝlǝna mǝlulle.
\v 21 Lang ǝn nying ban mǝnia ka, mǝ ndanǝ agir kpǝm, sǝama Yahweh nyesǝnam nǝ ɓabuam atàrǝì. Palang sǝ wu tunǝam ama Naomi, yi mǝnana Ɓakuli mana Karban nǝ Gulo kat ka tsǝ̀ngŋǝ̀nám aɓa tanni, sǝ yinanǝ murɓikea amuram ngga?>>
\p 
\v 22 Anggo sǝ Naomi nyarî nzali Mowap andǝ Rut ɓwama'Mowap, nkili-mǝɓwame. À yi bik Betalami, a bàkú mǝnana aɓwe tita pwan mǝssa-bálì nǝi ka.
\c 2
\s1 Rut pàktúró a ɓaban mala Boaz
\p 
\v 1 Naomi ka ndanǝ ɓè ɓǝla mala burí, lùllǝì ama Boaz. Yì Boaz ka ɓwamǝgule na, sǝ mǝkume na a nggurkwar mala Elimelek.
\v 2 A ɓè pwari ka, Rut ɓwama'Mowap banggi Naomi ama, <<Ida earâm mǝ kya alta ɓakurikuri mala mǝssa mǝnana amǝtúró ɗeki arǝ aɓaban ngga, atà ɓwa mǝnana kat nǝ̀ earam mǝ pàktúró atè ka.>>
\p Naomi earî wi ama, <<Kyane, muna-ɓwama mem.>>
\p 
\v 3 Nda Rut puro wari arǝ aɓaban, sǝ kǝ gya anzǝm amǝ'túró can mǝssa, aban alta ɓakurikuri. Rut yi kum ɓamúrì a ɓaban mala Boaz. \fig Rut wari aban alta ɓakurikuri|alt="Rut went to glean" src="08_Ruth2.2_Gleaning.jpg" size="col" loc="Rut 2:3" copy="Cook OT" ref="2:1-3"\fig*
\p 
\v 4 Zuku ka, Boaz pur a Betalami sǝ yiu [ace sǝn amǝ'túró a ɓaban], sǝ makkia-wia-kún ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ Yahweh pa atà wun.>> À nyesǝi wi ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ Yahweh tsǝko bù.>>
\p 
\v 5 Pǝlǝa Boaz ɗì mǝgulo amur amǝ'túró male ama, <<Ya lo ɓwama na mǝno?>>
\p 
\v 6 Ɓwabure earî wi ama, <<Lo ɓwama'Mowap mǝnana yiu atārǝia andǝ Naomi lang nyarî nzali Mowap ka nda.
\v 7 Ɓwame zǝmbam ama mǝ nyi ɓǝ̀ kǝ gya anzǝm amǝ'túró, ace alta ɓakurikuri mala mǝssa. Twal a dǝmbari ka, camarǝ pàktúró, she adyan tù sǝ tamsǝ túró ace usǝlǝ bǝti a yilǝm.>>
\p 
\v 8 Pǝlǝa Boaz ne Rut ama, <<Kwakikiro, muna-ɓwama mem. Kǝa na ama a nǝ ká alta ɓakurikuri a ɓè ɓaban ko awu nǝ nying ɓaban man ɗang. Ue kani atà mamǝna amǝtúró mem.
\v 9 Tsǝk-mǝsǝo arǝ ban mǝnana aburana kǝ can mǝssa kàm ngga, sǝ wu kpa ateà wun nǝ̀ amamǝna amǝtúró mem. Ən nani alaggana mem ama ɓǝà kǝa jeo ɗang. Sǝ ɓǝ̀ mǝsamur walo ka, kya ɗàrǝ́ mùr aɓalǝ adú mǝnana à lùmsǝkia ka, wu nu.>>
\p 
\v 10 Rut kūndǝ nǝ ɓamǝsǝi a nzali, sǝ ne Boaz ama, <<Palang sǝ ǝn kum earmúrú a bano anggo? Palang sǝ a lǝmdǝi bǝriɓwa pěmǝɓoarne anggo kǝ̀rkǝ́r?>>
\p 
\v 11 Boaz eari wi ama, <<Ən ongŋǝna cau mala gìr mǝnana kat a pakkì nkilo-mǝɓwame, tite a pwari mǝnana burio pàngŋǝ̀nà-lú nǝi ka. À banggam ama a nying tárró andǝ nggó, andǝ nzali-la mô, sǝ a yiu ace do aɓalǝ aɓwana mǝnana a súrǝ̀ia ɗiɗyal raka.
\v 12 Ɓǝ̀ Yahweh mbweo tangnakusǝo ace gìr mǝnana a pàk ka. Ɓǝ̀ Yahweh Ɓakuli mala Isǝrayila mǝnana a yina abani ace kum ban-auwa ka, mbweo tangnakusǝo kat!>>
\p 
\v 13 Rut nyesǝi wi ama, <<Ɓwamǝgule, a lǝmdǝnam pěmǝɓoarne. A tsǝ́ngŋǝ̀nám rǝam pwalǝna ɗwal nǝ cau mǝɓukɓuki mǝnana a nam ngga, kat andǝ amani ama ǝn pa aɓalǝ guro mò raka.>>
\p 
\v 14 Lang pwari li girlina pángŋǝ̀nà ka, Boaz ne Rut ama, <<Yiu ak girlina, lǐ sǝ wu nu mùr ɓǝlanggun anap.>> Nda Rut do andǝ amǝ'túró can mǝssa, sǝ Boaz pe wi mǝssa mǝnana à dandǝi ka. Rut lìli ɗǝmbo, cili girlina ueo.
\v 15-16 Lang Rut longŋǝna nǝ̀ nyar aban alta ɓakurikuri ka, Boaz ne alaggana male ama, <<Wu nying Rut ɓǝ̀ alta ɓakurikuri a ban mǝnana akúnò mǝssa ram kam ngga. Wu kǝa pǝrki ɗàng. Ɗǝm ngga, wu pusǝ aɓea amur-mǝssa arǝ akúnò, sǝ wu nyia ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ tarkia ka.>>
\p 
\v 17 Nda Rut lidǝmba nǝ ram ɓakurikuri a ɓaban ba pwarikpǝra ka; sǝ lang nyána mǝssa mǝnana ram ngga, kum mǝsǝsa mǝnana lùmsǝ nggea-kwar ka.
\v 18 Pǝlǝa twal mǝsǝse umnǝi a là, kya lǝmdǝi nkili-mǝɓwame gulo mala mǝsǝsa mǝnana ram ngga. Ɗǝm ngga, pè nkili-mǝɓwame girlina mana lì sǝ cili ue ka.
\v 19 Naomi ɗì ama, <<Nda aya ban, sǝ a ram mǝssa mǝnia kat yalung? A ɓaban mala yana sǝ a pàktúró? Ɓǝ̀ Ɓakuli tsǝki ɓwabura mǝnana lǝmdǝo earmúrú ka bù.>>
\p Rut ne Naomi ama nda a ɓaban mala ɓè ɓwabura lullǝi ama Boaz sǝ ram ɓakurikuri.
\p 
\v 20 Naomi banggi Rut nkili-mǝɓwame ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ tsǝkbu sulǝ amurí nǝban Yahweh mǝnana bwal domǝsǝcau andǝ pěmǝɓoarne male aban aɓwana mǝnana nǝyilǝmu ka andǝ aɓwana mana à wuna ka.\f + \fr 2:20 \fq aban aɓwana mǝnana nǝyilǝmu ka andǝ aɓwana mana à wuna ka \ft ko <<aban sǝm mǝnana sǝm ndanǝ yilǝmu ka andǝ abura sǝm mǝnana à wukina ka>>\f*>> Pǝlǝa Naomi banggi wi ama, <<Ɓwabura mǝno ka ɓǝla-nggurkwar ma'sǝma. Yì ka nda mwashat aɓalǝ amǝ'akmúr sǝm.>>
\p 
\v 21 Ɗǝm ngga Rut ɓwama'Mowap na ama, <<Yale ɓwabure banggam ama, <Ue kani atà amǝ'túró mem sheɓǝ̀ à malna pwan-gìrɓaban mem kat ka.> >>
\p 
\v 22 Naomi ne Rut, nkili-mǝɓwame ama, <<E, muna-ɓwama mem, nǝ̀ ɓoaribani wu pàktúró wunǝ amamǝna amǝtúró mala Boaz. Ɓǝ̀ a o a ɓaban mala ɓeɓwa ɗàng ngga, ɓekǝ gìr mǝɓane nǝ̀ gandǝnǝ kumo.>>
\v 23 Nda Rut pàktúró a nkanggari amamǝna amǝtúró mala Boaz aban ram ɓakurikuri ateà, ba masǝlǝata pwan-gìrɓaban mala mǝssa-bálì andǝ mala mǝssa-alkama kat. Anzǝm mǝno ka, Rut do andǝ nkili-mǝɓwame.
\c 3
\s1 Naomi kumbi Rut bura
\p 
\v 1 A ɓè pwari ka, Naomi banggi Rut, nkili-mǝɓwame ama, <<Muna-ɓwama mem, pà nǝ̀ ɓoaro mǝ kumbo usǝlǝo, ace mǝnana koman ngga ɓǝ̀ kyanbo pepè ka re?\f + \fr 3:1 \fq pà nǝ̀ ɓoaro mǝ kumbo usǝlǝo, ace mǝnana koman ngga ɓǝ̀ kyanbo pepè ka re? \ft Ko <<Pà nǝ̀ ɓoaro mǝ kumbo bura ace mǝnana wu kum ɓala mò ka re?>>\f*
\v 2 Ɗenyi ama mǝnia yì ɓwabura, yì Boaz mǝnana a kǝ wari a paktúró wunǝ amamǝna amǝtúró male ka, ɓǝla-nggurkwar ma'sǝma. Ado ka, kwakikiro. Nǝ pwarikpǝra man ngga, amǝtúró nǝ̀ nyaki wi mǝssa-bálì male a katǝra.
\v 3 Acemani ka, sussǝo, hasǝ mùrú, sǝ wu oasǝ agir-nggūrǝu mô mǝɓoarne-katkat. Pǝlǝa wu kya a ban mǝnana à kǝ̀ nya mǝssa kam ngga, sǝama kǝa eari wi ɓǝ̀ sǝlǝ ama a nda a ban mǝno ɗàng, sheɓǝ̀ malǝna lǐ andǝ nu ka.
\v 4 Tsǝkiro pepè wu sǝn ban mǝnana nǝ̀ nong kam ngga. Anzǝm mana kongŋǝna a ntulo ka, kya loasǝ nggubyau-kùmsǝo male, sǝ wu nong tù a ban akusǝi. Yì ka nǝ̀ banggo gìr mǝnana awu nǝ pàk ka.>>
\p 
\v 5 Rut earî Naomi ama, <<Mǝ nǝ pàk gìr mǝnana kat a banggam ama mǝ pak ka.>>
\p 
\v 6 Nda Rut wari a ban nya mǝssa, sǝ pàk gìr mǝnana kat nkili-mǝɓwame ne wi ama ɓǝ̀ pàk ka.
\v 7 Lang Boaz malǝna lǐ andǝ nu ka, banɓoari wi. Sǝ wari a ban mǝnana à ramgi akúnò mǝssa-bálì ka, sǝ nongŋo nǝ̀ nong'ntullo. Pǝlǝa Rut ging zàng, kya loasǝ nggubyau-kùmsǝo mala Boaz, sǝ nong tù a ban akusǝi.
\v 8 Nǝ ɓadu ka, Boaz lo hǝrkit, sǝ lang pǝlǝ ka, ndali, sǝn ɓè ɓwama aban nongŋo a ban akusǝi!
\v 9 Boaz ɗì ama, <<A nda yana?>>
\p Pǝlǝa ɓwame ear ama, <<Mǝ nda guro mò, Rut. Sárǝ́ nggubyau mô amuram, acemǝnana a nda mǝ'akmúrú ka.\f + \fr 3:9 \fq Sárǝ́ nggubyau mô amuram, acemǝnana a nda mǝ'akmúrú ka; \ft ko <<Alǎm, acemǝnana a nda ɓǝla-nggurkwar mǝnana nda a ɓabuo wu ɗenyi nǝ ɓwa kǝla mim, mǝnana burém, ɓǝla mô wuna ka.>>\f*>>
\v 10 Boaz ne wi ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ Yahweh tsǝko bù, muna-ɓwama mem. Gìr mǝnia a kǝ pè ado ka, a ndaban lǝmdǝ domǝsǝcau mǝgule mǝnana kútì mana a lǝmdǝì nkilo-mǝɓwame ka. Ɓǝ́ a umǝna alta lagga-ɓwa mǝkume ko mǝ'tǝ̀r, sǝama a pak anggo ɗàng.
\v 11 Ado ka, cè ɓangciu pakko ɗàng ɓoarnsarilem. Mǝ nǝ pàk gìr mǝnana kat a bang ngga. Acili aɓwana mǝnana kat a là ka, à sǝlǝna ama a nda ɓwama mǝɓoarne.
\v 12 Mǝsǝcau na ama mǝ nda mǝ'akmúrú, sǝama ɓeɓwa nakam mǝnana nda a dǝmbanǝ mim kǝla ɓǝla-nggurkwar ka.
\v 13 Ue kani a dù man yalung ngga. Sǝ lí nǝ dǝmbari ka, sǝm nǝ̀ ɗì. Ɓǝ̀ eare nǝ̀ akmuro ka, mǝɓoarne na. Sǝ ɓǝ̀ earce nǝ̀ pàk anggo raka, ǝn panacau a bano ama, mbak-kàngkàng Yahweh nakam ngga, mǝ nǝ akmuro. Ado ka, nong kani sheɓǝ̀ bankwarna ka.>>
\p 
\v 14 Nda Rut nong kano nǝban akusǝ Boaz, sǝama kaniama ban nǝ̀ kwaro mǝnana ɓwa nǝ̀ gandǝ sǝn ɓì nǝ̀ súrǝì ka, Rut loapi ban mǝno. Boaz ka earce ama kǝɓwa ɓǝ̀ sǝlǝ ama ɓè ɓwama yiu kani a ban nya mǝssa ɗàng.
\v 15 Boaz ne wi ama, <<Yinǝ nggubyau-koarǝu mô, sǝ wu sárǝi kani.>> Rut pǝlǝa pàk anggo, sǝ Boaz karǝkì wi mǝssa-bálì tasau tongno-nong-mwashat aɓa nggubyau-koarǝu, sǝ tsǝki wi amurí. Pǝlǝa Rut nyar a là nǝ mǝsǝsa mǝno.
\p 
\v 16 Lang Rut yiu a ɓala aban Naomi nkili-mǝɓwame ka, Naomi ɗì ama, <<Muna-ɓwama mem, wu kya mal lang le?>>
\p Pǝlǝa Rut ne wi gìr mǝnana kat Boaz pàk aceì ka.
\v 17 Nyare ne wi ɗǝm ama, <<Boaz banggam ama mǝ nggá nyar a bano nǝ ɓabuam atàrǝì ɗàng, nda pam mǝnia yì mǝssa-bálì kat ka.>>
\p 
\v 18 Pǝlǝa Naomi banggi wi ama, <<Ado ka, kúndǝô, muna-ɓwama mem, sheɓǝ̀ a sǝna gìr mǝnana nǝ̀ pur aɓalǝi ka. Boaz pà nǝ̀ usǝlǝ yalung ɗàng, sheɓǝ̀ malna cê ka.>>
\c 4
\s1 Boaz akmúr Rut
\p 
\v 1 Boaz wari a [ban ramba mala aɓwana] a kún là, sǝ dumnǝdo abanì. Pǝlǝa ɓè ɓǝla-nggurkwar, yì ɓwabura mǝnana Boaz bangcau male aban Rut ka, yiu kǝ kútiô; sǝ Boaz tunǝi ama, <<Gyajam mem, kàra yiu, yi dumnǝdo kani.>> Ɓwabure pǝlǝa kàra wario kya dumnǝdo.
\v 2 Sǝ Boaz tunǝ aɓwana-mǝgule lum mala lê, sǝ banggia wia ama ɓǝà dumnǝdo gbal. Lang à dumǝna ka,
\v 3 Boaz ne ɓǝla-nggurkwar male ama, <<Ado mǝnana Naomi nyarǝnì nzali Mowap ka, kǝ earce ama nǝ̀ mak nzali mala ɓǝla ma'sǝm Elimelek,
\v 4 sǝ ǝn sǝni ka, ndanǝ ɓoaro wu sǝlǝa. Ado ka, ɓǝ̀ a kǝ earce ka, kúrí aɓadǝm aburana mǝnia à dumnǝdo kani ka, sǝ aɓadǝm aɓwana-mǝgule mala aɓwana mem. Sǝ ɓǝ̀ a kǝ earce raka, na kúno mǝ sǝlǝa, acemǝnana a nda ɓwa mǝnana ɓoaro wu kúrí ka. Anzǝmó ka, mǝ nda.>>
\p Ɓwabure ear ama, <<Mǝ nǝ kúrí.>>
\p 
\v 5 Pǝlǝa Boaz banggi wi ama, <<Ndanǝ ɓoaro, sǝama a pwari mǝnana a nǝ kúr nzalinì a bù Naomi ka, awu nǝ twal Rut yì mā-lú ɓwama'Mowap gbal, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ nzali liɓalanî ueo a bù aɓwana mala lú ka.>>
\p 
\v 6 Ɓwabure eari wi ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ cê na anggo ka, pà mǝ nǝ kúr nzalinì ɗǝm ɗàng, acemǝnana nzalinì pà nǝ̀ duk nzali liɓala mala amunem ɗàng. Kúrí, acemǝnana pà mǝ nǝ gandǝ akmúrí ɗàng.>>
\p 
\v 7 A nza mǝno ka, kuncau mala amǝ'Isǝrayila amur cau mala akmúr nzali ko mê ka, nda mǝnana ama: ɓwa mǝnana kǝ mak nzali ka, nǝ̀ pusǝ nkura male a kusǝi, sǝ nǝ̀ pè ɓwa mǝnana nǝ kúr nzalinì ka. Anggo sǝ amǝ Isǝrayila kǝ lǝmdǝ ama cê ka dumǝna.
\p 
\v 8 Acemani ka, lang ɓwabure ne Boaz ama, <<Kúrí>> ka, pusǝ nkura male pè Boaz.
\v 9 Pǝlǝa Boaz banggi aɓwana-mǝgule andǝ acili aɓwana mǝnana a ban mǝno ka ama, <<Yalung ngga, wu dumǝna amǝ'nakún kat ama, ǝn kúrna gìr mǝnana kat mala Elimelek na, andǝ gir mǝnana kat mala amuna-burana male, yià Kiliyon andǝ Malon na ka.
\v 10 Ɗǝm ngga, Rut ɓwama'Mowap, yì mā-lú mala Malon, pǝlǝna māmám, ace ɓǝlî lú muna mǝnana nǝ̀ yia liɓala male ka, ace mǝnana lullǝ lú ɓǝ̀ kǝa ndǝrmì ɓalǝ aɓǝla-nggurkwar male andǝ là male raka. Wu nda ka amǝ'nakún, a pwari man yalung ngga.>>
\p 
\v 11 Aɓwana-mǝgule andǝ aɓwana mǝnana kat à nda a ban ramba a kún lá kà à bang ama, <<E, sǝm nda ka amǝ'nakún. Ɓǝ̀ Yahweh tsǝk ɓwama mǝnia kǝ yiu a kútiô a ɓala mò ka ɓǝ̀ duk kǝla Rahila andǝ Liya, mǝnana nǝbania yià kǝm sǝ à kum ɓwapǝndǝa mala ɓala Isǝrayila ka. Ɓǝ̀ Yahweh tsǝa wu hangǝli\f + \fr 4:11 \fq wu hangǝli \ft ko <<wu duk mǝgǝna>>\f* a Efǝrata, sǝ ɓǝ̀ lullǝo zǝki a Betalami.
\v 12 Ɓǝ̀ Yahweh tsǝa amuna mǝnana nsari man nǝ̀ ɓǝlô ka, à nǝ̀ tsǝk ɓala mò ɓǝ̀ pa kǝla ɓala mala Perez, muna-ɓwabura mala Yahuda mǝnana ɓǝl andǝ Tamar ka.>>
\s1 Boaz andǝ nggurkwar male
\p 
\v 13 Nda Boaz twal Rut pǝlǝ māmí ka. Yahweh tsǝki Rut bù, kum muna a bumi sǝ ɓǝl muna-ɓwabura.
\v 14 Amamǝna mala Betalami ne Naomi ama, <<Ɓwangsǝban ɓǝ pà aban Yahweh! Yalung ngga, Yahweh pano mǝ'kau muna-ɓwabura ace tsǝkiro. Ɓǝ̀ Yahweh tsǝa ɓǝ̀ lullǝ mune zǝki a Isǝrayila!
\v 15 Nkilo-mǝɓwame mǝnana kǝ earceo, sǝ pàngŋǝ́nò gìr mǝnana kútì mǝnana amuna-burana tongno-nong-ɓari nǝ̀ pàkkô ka. Sǝ ado ka, ɓǝlǝno mǝ'kau muna-ɓwabura mǝnana nǝ̀ yinǝo nǝ bǝsa yilǝmu, sǝ nǝ̀ tsǝkiro aɓa è mô ka.>>
\v 16 Naomi twal mune, nongsǝi a byali, sǝ iulǝi.
\p 
\v 17 Amamǝna mǝnana à nda murkala andǝia ka, à tsǝkî mune lullǝu ama Obet. À bang ama, <<À ɓǝlǝni Naomi muna-ɓwabura!>>
\p Obet na yi ɓǝl Jeshi, sǝ Jeshi yi bǝl Dauda ka.
\p 
\v 18-22 Mǝnia ka nda nggurkwar mala Perez:
\li1 Perez nda tár Hezǝron,
\li1 Hezǝron nda tár Ram,
\li1 Ram nda tár Aminadap,
\li1 Aminadap nda tár Nashon,
\li1 Nashon nda tár Salmon,
\li1 Salmon nda tár Boaz,
\li1 Boaz nda tár Obet,
\li1 Obet nda tár Jeshi,
\li1 Sǝ Jeshi nda tár Dauda.
